Interface ChildNetInterfaceBusLoad

    public interface ChildNetInterfaceBusLoad
extends ChildNetInterfaceBus
    A representation of the model object 'Child Net Interface Bus Load'. Interface bus load for defining parnet-child interface.

    • Load Id Pair
